attachments.title: Inside the Groan-Inducing World of Pun Competitions
attachments.text: Our writer dove into the linguistic thunderdome of wordplay battles. The English language will never be the same.
attachments.fallback: WIRED: Inside the Groan-Inducing World of Pun Competitions

text: > “I’ve often compared punsters to linguistic terrorists,” Hallock says. “We’re literally stalking conversations, looking for the weak place to plant our bomb.”
